"Uh, yeah," he says between puff, trying to put out the flames. He lets go
of Killfest, and transforms back to car mode. Still on fire, he races to
the ground, Gravity pulling him hard. He hits the ground hard, but the
speed of his decent puts out the fire. He drives forward, following
Killfest from below.
